1
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:38,720
♪The waves of sword dance send out ripples♪

2
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:41,560
♪I weather the raging storm to chase after the victorious banner♪

3
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:44,920
♪The snow is not concerned with joy or sadness♪

4
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:47,920
♪The horse rein I have been holding falls apart in the desert♪

5
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:51,040
♪My greenness is not an excuse to be bullied♪

6
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:54,200
♪Spreading the wings and soaring, inviting recklessness at any moment♪

7
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:57,200
♪I do not fear the life of hardship♪

8
00:00:57,280 --> 00:01:00,040
♪For I shall solve all riddles destined for me♪

9
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:03,400
♪Great difficulties can summon the sea of courage♪

10
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:06,640
♪It's worth defending heroic spirits in the martial arts world♪

11
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:12,000
♪One smile is all it takes, I travel faraway with my spirited ballads♪

12
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:15,820
♪Chasing after the hot-blooded dreams♪

13
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,880
♪Growing old with a heart of gold♪

14
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,000
♪The journey ahead will leave scars♪

15
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:25,000
♪A life is only worth living with adventures♪

16
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:28,320
♪Conflicts are witnessed by the clashing of youths♪

17
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:31,080
♪Brushing against the blade of time♪

18
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:38,040
♪At the end of the universe, we embark on another journey yet again♪

19
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,760
♪Chasing after the hot-blooded dreams♪

20
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:43,760
♪Growing old with a heart of gold♪

21
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:46,680
♪The journey ahead will leave scars♪

22
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:50,400
♪A life is only worth living with adventures♪

23
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:53,120
♪Conflicts are witnessed by the clashing of youths♪

24
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:56,000
♪Brushing against the blade of time♪

25
00:01:56,400 --> 00:02:03,480
♪At the end of the universe, we embark on another journey yet again♪

26
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:15,940
[The Blood of Youth: Quest of Heroic Hearts]

27
00:02:15,980 --> 00:02:18,980
[Episode 11]

28
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:22,400
Read what you wrote.

29
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,240
What purpose do they serve?

30
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,590
They can't bring you fortune.

31
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:31,710
They are only barely enough to feed your worthless, miserable life.

32
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,630
But your life

33
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,560
is meaningless.

34
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,870
Who gets to decide what a meaningful life is?

35
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:40,190
Definitely not

36
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,590
a coward

37
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:43,800
who doesn't dare to show their face like you!

38
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,680
What did you say?

39
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:48,750
You don't even understand what I'm saying.

40
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:50,960
What makes you think

41
00:02:51,590 --> 00:02:53,400
you have the right to mock me?

42
00:02:59,340 --> 00:03:00,260
[Tear]

43
00:03:00,260 --> 00:03:01,620
[Away]

44
00:03:01,620 --> 00:03:02,420
[Brush]

45
00:03:02,420 --> 00:03:03,780
[My brush is my blade]

46
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:05,190
What are you doing?

47
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,750
What are you doing?

48
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,240
[Blade]

49
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,030
Impressive.

50
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:11,280
"My brush is my blade, tearing away all the injustices."

51
00:03:12,150 --> 00:03:13,710
I shall break your sword.

52
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,400
Without your brush,

53
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:18,240
you won't be able to write.

54
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,630
You are a humiliation of Lei's Stronghold.

55
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:28,280
Your life serves no purpose.

56
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:30,430
You might as well

57
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:34,360
let me take your place.

58
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:46,260
[My brush is my blade, tearing away all the injustices.]

59
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:53,860
[Injus...]

60
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,150
You don't need a brush to write.

61
00:03:58,150 --> 00:03:59,400
You just need your heart.

62
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,400
As long as my heart continues to beat,

63
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,470
I can keep

64
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:06,150
creating.

65
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,960
In my world,

66
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,960
you're as good as dead!

67
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,510
Why struggle?

68
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:56,510
A quick death is better than a futile resistance.

69
00:04:58,120 --> 00:05:00,040
I've sharpened my blade.

70
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:02,480
Your suffering will soon be over.

71
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:09,040
Compared to being shackled by your memories,

72
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:11,560
death should be

73
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,600
a better option for you,

74
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,720
right?

75
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,630
Weigui.

76
00:05:22,430 --> 00:05:23,040
Weigui.

77
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,000
Weigui!

78
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,270
Be trapped in the past

79
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,240
or die now.

80
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,360
Those are the options you give me.

81
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,310
But only I

82
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,430
get to imprison myself.

83
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,000
You appeared

84
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:47,430
in my dream many times.

85
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,480
You're just my inner demon.

86
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:52,630
If you are just a part of me,

87
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,800
then I shall fear you no longer.

88
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,000
Master told me

89
00:06:30,070 --> 00:06:31,510
that some would progress faster than I.

90
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,950
But I can always catch up.

91
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:37,000
Strongest swordsman, you say?

92
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,240
It is a tall order,

93
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:41,190
but one that I will achieve.

94
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,120
Given your capability,

95
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,270
you can't even be

96
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:49,720
the strongest swordsman if you have ten lives.

97
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,360
And your fool of a master.

98
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:56,800
He can fantasize very well,

99
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,830
and you just take everything at face value.

100
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:06,480
Since the beginning,

101
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:08,240
you've been belittling me.

102
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:09,720
And now,

103
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:11,800
you're insulting my master.

104
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:15,720
You want to make me angry.

105
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:19,270
Why should I unsheathe this sword?

106
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:21,040
What purpose

107
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,120
does it serve?

108
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,000
If you unsheathe it, you can kill everyone.

109
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,950
What is there to be proud of?

110
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,120
In this martial arts world,

111
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:31,360
people kill those who oppose,

112
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,600
spare those who submit.

113
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:35,950
The strongest swordsman?

114
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:37,190
That's just a vanity title.

115
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:39,480
I practice martial arts

116
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,510
not to kill,

117
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,070
but to save.

118
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:48,040
The martial arts world

119
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:50,750
isn't about fleeing,

120
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,040
but

121
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,000
protecting.

122
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,600
Is someone there?

123
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,430
Is someone there?

124
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:18,680
Lei Lingze.

125
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,120
I can't believe

126
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,120
you got out of the illusion.

127
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:25,390
If you could do it,

128
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:26,510
why couldn't I?

129
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,630
Where's Hua Xiaohua?

130
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,360
She isn't out yet.

131
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,910
Don't worry about her.

132
00:08:34,550 --> 00:08:35,240
It's just

133
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,720
a matter of time.

134
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,790
That is...

135
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:02,630
What is that?

136
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:06,720
Is it

137
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:09,550
the legendary

138
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:11,150
Skysplitter?

139
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,200
Skysplitter?

140
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:16,480
Then, are the fragments we collected

141
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:17,840
fake?

142
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,670
That's right.

143
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,390
Divine Maiden.

144
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:30,000
The Skysplitter fragments are all fake.

145
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,600
The Skysplitter before you

146
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:33,510
is the real one.

147
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,510
Divine Maiden.

148
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,480
Lei Lingze.

149
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:58,360
Weigui!

150
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:15,220
[Corridor Keeper]

151
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,080
Who are you?

152
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:21,000
A name is just a tag with which you differentiate others.

153
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:23,000
I have long forgotten my name.

154
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:25,720
So cryptic.

155
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,320
Why are you in my way?

156
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,000
I'm here to save you.

157
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:32,960
You inherited your master's mantle.

158
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,750
So why are you wreaking havoc here?

159
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:36,360
That is my choice.

160
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:37,840
It has nothing to do with my master.

161
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,870
Are you aware of the consequences?

162
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:44,120
Your power went rogue after you forced your way through the inner demon.

163
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:45,910
Without the suppression from my flute,

164
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:47,750
you will die from exhaustion.

165
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,320
I don't care.

166
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:53,480
The inner demon you cannot escape from

167
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:55,150
is your destiny.

168
00:10:57,870 --> 00:10:58,790
Unfortunately,

169
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:00,750
I do not believe in destiny.

170
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:16,080
Sir,

171
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:17,510
are you a friend or a foe?

172
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:20,120
In terms of seniority,

173
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:21,630
both of you

174
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:22,870
should call me

175
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,120
Grandmaster.

176
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,270
You must be here to look for the sword.

177
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:35,390
You recognize me?

178
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,600
The owner of the Skysplitter once told me

179
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,840
that you'd be here to retrieve the sword.

180
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,440
Where is he now?

181
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,960
He merely told me to give the sword to you.

182
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,240
But before that,

183
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:50,390
I need you

184
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:51,750
to do something.

185
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:53,840
Forget it.

186
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,480
What if the sword is fake?

187
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:57,120
Our effort will be in vain.

188
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:02,720
Skysplitter is a divine sword.

189
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,480
It will never break.

190
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:06,750
Jinxuan said that

191
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,480
to lure him out.

192
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:10,360
But who knew

193
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:12,360
so many would fall for it?

194
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,550
In that case,

195
00:12:15,270 --> 00:12:17,240
what do you want me to do?

196
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,550
I want both of you to bring Xiao Se

197
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,480
back to the martial arts world.

198
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:24,510
Both of us?

199
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,390
And me too.

200
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,030
Hua Xiaohua.

201
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:30,870
Hua Xiaohua?

202
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:10,400
♪How can I make peace when time♪

203
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:13,520
♪Only leaves me with my shadow?♪

204
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:18,480
♪Yet the intertwining bonds in my life♪

205
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:21,760
♪Render me blind♪

206
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:26,680
♪I was once naive and innocent♪

207
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:29,960
♪Seeking a soul with whom to dance♪

208
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:34,920
♪Yet my life is like a wisp of smoke♪

209
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:38,080
♪Scattered by a gust of wind♪

210
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:41,080
♪In this life, I am not destined to be understood♪

211
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:43,360
♪But misunderstood♪

212
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:46,440
♪I do not know sincerity♪

213
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:51,200
♪If the river of time could flow back to its starting point♪

214
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:54,520
♪Let's not meet again♪

215
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:57,480
♪No one will be able to understand me♪

216
00:13:57,880 --> 00:13:59,560
♪None will go as I wish♪

217
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:02,800
♪How I long for that one moment to last forever♪

218
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:07,520
♪All mortal obsessions turn into dusts of nothingness♪

219
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:10,720
♪Let's not meet in another life♪

220
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:14,400
♪Not in another life♪

221
